      <description>&lt;!--&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center; padding-top:2rem;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/profile_picture.png&#34; style=&#34;width:150px; border-radius:50%;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h1 style=&#34;margin:0.5rem 0 0;&#34;&gt;Ryder Hutchings&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div style=&#34;margin-top:12px; display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:20px; align-items:center;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://ryderhutchings.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; style=&#34;color: var(--text-color);&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&#xA;    &lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ryderhutchings&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;https://cdn.simpleicons.org/github/2a2524/bdd0cf&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://youtube.com/@ryderhutchings&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;https://cdn.simpleicons.org/youtube/2a2524/bdd0cf&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://tiktok.com/@ryderhutchings&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;https://cdn.simpleicons.org/tiktok/2a2524/bdd0cf&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://instagram.com/ryderhutchings_&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img src=&#34;https://cdn.simpleicons.org/instagram/2a2524/bdd0cf&#34; width=&#34;24&#34; height=&#34;24&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;--&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hi! I&amp;rsquo;m Ryder and welcome to my website. I built this with Hugo + Hugo ʕ•ᴥ•ʔ Bear Blog around one idea: the interwebs should be simple again. Minimal, fast, and zero Ads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
