    <item>
      <title>About</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hey, I&amp;rsquo;m Ryder. I&amp;rsquo;m a small content creator and business owner. I review technology, share tutorials, and create videos about my hobbies and interests.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ve been making YouTube videos across various channels for 6 years now.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Outside of the interwebs, I love running. My mile PR is &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8db0af;&#34;&gt;5:39.21&lt;/span&gt; and my 5K PR is &lt;span style=&#34;color:#8db0af;&#34;&gt;20:08.9&lt;/span&gt;. I plan to attempt (and hopefully complete multiple) marathons at some point in my life. I also enjoy learning about electronics and plan to study Computer and Electrical Engineering.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
